        "shortDescription": "<p> Route specific URL patterns to different origins (e.g., <code>/api/*</code> → Lambda, <code>/assets/*</code> → S3).</p>\n",
        "longDescription": "<p>Evaluated in order; first match wins. Unmatched requests go to the default origin.\nEach route can have its own caching and forwarding settings.</p>\n",
