        "shortDescription": "<p> The URL path that will trigger this integration.</p>\n",
        "longDescription": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Exact path</strong>: <code>/users</code></li>\n<li><strong>Path with parameter</strong>: <code>/users/{id}</code>. The <code>id</code> will be available in <code>event.pathParameters.id</code>.</li>\n<li><strong>Greedy path</strong>: <code>/files/{proxy+}</code>. This will match any path starting with <code>/files/</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n",
