        "longDescription": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Fargate</strong> (set <code>cpu</code> + <code>memory</code>): Serverless, no servers to manage.</li>\n<li><strong>EC2</strong> (set <code>instanceTypes</code>): Choose specific instance types for more control or GPU access.</li>\n</ul>\n",
