        "longDescription": "<p>The path to the file where the directive is defined, in the format <code>{file-path}:{handler}</code>.</p>\n<p>If the <code>{handler}</code> is omitted:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>For <code>.js</code> and <code>.ts</code> files, the <code>default</code> export is used.</li>\n<li>For <code>.py</code> files, the <code>main</code> function is used.</li>\n</ul>\n",
