        "longDescription": "<ul>\n<li><strong><code>stacktape-lambda-buildpack</code></strong> (recommended): Point to your source file and Stacktape builds,\nbundles, and uploads it automatically.</li>\n<li><strong><code>custom-artifact</code></strong>: Provide a pre-built zip file. Stacktape handles the upload.</li>\n</ul>\n",
