        "longDescription": "<p>All traffic is encrypted in transit. Use <code>$Secret()</code> instead of hardcoding:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-yaml\">defaultUserPassword: $Secret(&#39;redis.password&#39;)\n</code></pre>\n",
