        "longDescription": "<p>ARN of an ACM certificate in <strong>us-east-1</strong> to use for this domain.\nBy default, Stacktape uses the certificate associated with your domain in us-east-1.</p>\n<p>The certificate must be in us-east-1 because Cognito uses CloudFront for custom domains.</p>\n",
