        "longDescription": "<p>Attaches a regional firewall directly to the service&#39;s application load balancer.\nRequires <code>loadBalancing</code> type <code>application-load-balancer</code>.</p>\n<p>To protect a CDN-enabled service at CloudFront instead, use <code>cdn.useFirewall</code>\nwith a <code>web-app-firewall</code> resource whose <code>scope</code> is <code>cdn</code>.</p>\n",
